{"id":240,"date":"2025-03-16T22:37:21","date_gmt":"2025-03-16T15:37:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=240"},"modified":"2025-06-05T13:52:33","modified_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:52:33","slug":"hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da\/","title":{"rendered":"10+ c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2025"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau treatment, bong tr\u00f3c, m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 m\u00e3i ch\u01b0a ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i? <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eebng v\u1ed9i th\u1eed m\u1ecdi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. B\u00ed quy\u1ebft n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang <strong>ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/strong> &#8211; nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd b\u1eadt m\u00ed c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t &#8220;\u0111\u1ec9nh&#8221; nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2025 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-phuc-hoi-da-lai-quan-trong-trong-quy-trinh-cham-soc-da\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c sau khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd da. Khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u1edf n\u00ean y\u1ebfu \u1edbt v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c. <\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2519\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2519\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2519 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-la-gi-1.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-la-gi-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-la-gi-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-la-gi-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-la-gi-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2519\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da gi\u00fap l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u00fap da l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh sau nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"top-10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-dang-thu-nam-2025\"><\/span><strong>Top 10 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eed n\u0103m 2025<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed7i ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1eebng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a GSC, mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, c\u00f9ng xem ngay:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2521\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2521\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2521 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da.webp\" alt=\"Top 10 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eed n\u0103m 2025\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/10-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2521\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Top 10 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eed n\u0103m 2025<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhom-duong-am-va-bao-ve-da-toan-dien\"><\/span><em><strong>Nh\u00f3m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ceramides<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da Ceramides \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n v\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. Gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da khi chi\u1ebfm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda\u00a0 lipid l\u1edbp s\u1eebng. Khi da thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t ceramide, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da suy y\u1ebfu. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed vi\u00eam da. <\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed5 sung ceramide gi\u00fap kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng ch\u1eafn t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n da bong tr\u00f3c do d\u00f9ng treatment, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi b\u1ed5 sung ceramide, l\u00e0n da m\u1edbi d\u1ea7n kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ec1m m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hyaluronic Acid<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hyaluronic Acid (HA) v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t. M\u1ed9t ph\u00e2n t\u1eed HA c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea5p 1000 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh n\u00f3, gi\u00fap cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m s\u00e2u cho da, l\u00e0m m\u1ecbn c\u00e1c n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. Theo nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u1eeb Vi\u1ec7n Da li\u1ec5u Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (ISD), HA c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean da nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2518\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2518\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2518 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-2.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u00f3m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2518\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nh\u00f3m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Glycerin<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &#8220;th\u1ecfi nam ch\u00e2m h\u00fat \u1ea9m&#8221;, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i daGlycerin gi\u00fap h\u00fat \u1ea9m t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o da, duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 cho l\u00e0n da su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, Glycerin c\u00f2n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. GSC c\u0169ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y trong nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i cao c\u1ea5p GSC 2025<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhom-giam-viem-diu-da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><em><strong>Nh\u00f3m gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, d\u1ecbu da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Niacinamide- Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Niacinamide ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u201cchi\u1ebfn binh \u0111a n\u0103ng\u201d, v\u1eeba l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, niacinamide c\u00f2n k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t ceramide, gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, gi\u1eef \u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1eed s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a 5% Niacinamide khi da b\u1ecb m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau 2 tu\u1ea7n, l\u00e0n da \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Centella Asiatica (Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1)<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1 &#8211; th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da &#8211; gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0nh s\u1eb9o. Centella Asiatica c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p collagen, gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a GSC.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2517\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2517\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2517 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-1.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u00f3m gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, d\u1ecbu da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2517\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nh\u00f3m gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, d\u1ecbu da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allantoin<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allantoin n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a da, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhom-tai-tao-va-phuc-hoi-sau\"><\/span><em><strong>Nh\u00f3m t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i s\u00e2u<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Peptides<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Peptides l\u00e0 c\u00e1c chu\u1ed7i axit amin c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t collagen, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i. Nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng n\u00e0y, peptides g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m da tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lecithin<\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lecithin \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00f2a tan c\u00e1c vitamin c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho da. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung Lecithin gi\u00fap da tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-chon-hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-phu-hop\"><\/span><strong>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap da nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2520\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2520\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2520 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hoat-chat-phuc-hoi-da-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2520\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da: Da \u0111ang m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a?<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng: K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n kh\u00f4, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p ho\u1eb7c paraben, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu da b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u201cxoa d\u1ecbu\u201d m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c routine skincare, gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng m\u1ecdng, r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. Theo d\u00f5i GSC \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Da b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed1c h\u1ecfa, ng\u1ee9a r\u00e1t hay kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng m\u1ed7i khi thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi? N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1p \u00e1n l\u00e0 &#8220;c\u00f3&#8221;, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m &#8211; lo\u1ea1i da d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, m\u1ecfng manh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":2521,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[11,12],"class_list":["post-240","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-cham-soc-da","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/240","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=240"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/240\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3016,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/240\/revisions\/3016"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2521"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=240"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=240"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=240"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}